<td bgcolor=#ffffff>



<tt>&lt;scope&gt;</tt> is defined in the <i>Main RXML parser</i> module.
<p>
Creates a new scope for RXML variables. Variables can be changed within the
<tt>&lt;scope&gt;</tt> tag without having any effect outside it. 


<br clear=all>
<img src=/internal-roxen-unit width=1 height=10 alt="">

</td>
</tr>
